snippet.title: Project Nimbus: Code Mirai - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Project Nimbus: Code Mirai is an exciting mech-based flying game featuring vibrant graphics, blistering action gameplay and an epic storyline. Fly a variety of Battle Frames fighting enemies over floating cities, vast oceans, and in the reaches of space.

https://www.gametomo.co.jp/project-nimbus-en/
